:: Cook with Sebastian {"position":"2500,625","size":"100,100"}
* You offer to help cook with Seb
* Banter with Seb
* The top of the salt shaker comes off & all of the salt falls into the stew
* Small choice to help him fish the salt out, cover it with other spices, tease him, etc. (The specific options don't matter too much as long as the stew isn't thrown out or fixed in the end as this will be important in Act IV. The player's choice here should also result in a large affinity increase or decrease.)
* After the choice is made, the player can choose to help Kaya or Isaiah (if they haven't already) or eat.
* No obvious narrator yet, but narration is increasingly fourth-wall breaky.

