:: Eat {"position":"2500,775","size":"100,100"}
* With the tents set up, the fire going, & the air mattresses blown up, the group eats Seb's stew. It's, uhhh, not good.
* Include slightly tweaked versions depending on the protag's choices during the "Cook with Sebastian" node.
* Protag dialogue options should include supporting Seb vs teasing Seb.
* This one doesn't have a whole lot going on currently, so feel free to take some creative license! The only real requirements are that it tastes anywhere from weird to awful & that there's still stew left in the pot at the end.

